short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Pro2Pro browser extension test version

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Pro2Pro Browser Extension enables licensed Pro2Pro users to view and update their organization's processes, stages, and tasks.  Pro2Pro is a productivity solution for leaders allowing them to track, manage, and assign processes & checklists.

This is the TEST version of the Pro2Pro browser extension.
